lead_paragraph: Ellia Green has been cutting her teeth as a rugby player for four years in the pursuit of an Olympic gold medal. It has cost her a couple of teeth along the way, too.

headline.print_headline: Speedster Green Chasing Rugby Gold for Australia in Rio
